# Getting Support for AdvancedServerList
Please make sure to follow the below listed instructions to receive support with the plugin.

## Don't ask to ask, just ask!
Don't ask if anyone is around or could help. State your issue directly and wait for a reply.

## Check that the plugin is updated.
Make sure you use the latest plugin version supporting your server/proxy version.
Downloads can be found on [Modrinth](https://modrinth.com/plugin/advancedserverlist) and [HangarMC](https://hangar.papermc.io/Andre_601/AdvancedServerList).

*Supported Server/Proxy versions are 1.20.6+ for Paper-based Servers and 1.20.x+ for Proxies.*

## Explain your issue in detail
Explain your issue in as much detail as possible. Provide configurations and logs via paste sites and screenshots if it helps explaining your problem.

## Check the Wiki
The [AdvancedServerList Wiki](https://asl.andre601.ch) has many pages that answer common questions you may have.
Here are some recommended pages:

- [Getting Started Guide](https://asl.andre601.ch/getting-started)
- [Profile Options](https://asl.andre601.ch/profiles)
- [Commands](https://asl.andre601.ch/commands)
- [API Documentation](https://asl.andre601.ch/api)

## Be patient!
Support in this Discord is provided on a voluntary bases and "as is". Nobody, including the plugin dev, is obligated to help you and may even deny support for any or no reason given.
Any user may provide you with help. There is no guaranteed support by the plugin dev.
